    "Thus, we verified that CircDA has good predictive ability.",
    "Case analysis of diseases with unknown associated circRNAsTo verify the predictive performance of CircDA for diseases without known associated circRNAs, taking gastric cancer (GC) as an example, we first deleted all circRNA data associated with gastric cancer in the database then used the remaining circRNA-disease association data to train CircDA, and finally used the trained model to predict gastric cancer.",
    "The association scores with circRNAs were sorted, and the predicted top 20 circRNAs were verified.",
    "The results are shown in Fig. 4C.",
    "Among the top 20 circRNAs, 16 have been verified, and the 4 unverified circRNAs are also expected to be verified in future biological experiments."
